How to Prioritize Tasks Under Tight Deadlines?
When facing multiple tasks under pressure, using a structured approach helps you stay focused, avoid burnout, and meet deadlines efficiently. Hereâ€™s how:

1ï¸âƒ£ Identify and List All Tasks
Write down all tasks that need to be completed.
